data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in The Village at Heritage Park! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence is perfectly situated on a sprawling lot. 
Efficiency meets eco-consciousness with a fully paid-off solar system for energy savings to include a permitted EV charger plug type to power up your electric vehicle right at home. A brand-new heating and cooling system with a variable heat pump. 
Inside, the kitchen has been renovated, boasting modern amenities including new laminate flooring which complements the high vaulted ceilings. The bright and airy living spaces are perfect for entertaining. This home offers ample closets and built-in storage solutions. 
Location is key and this property offers easy access to Travis Air Force Base, HWY 12/ I-80, making your commute a breeze. Explore the beautiful surrounding areas of Napa and Sonoma, this home's location is a true convenience. This is a rare opportunity to own a home that marries style, sustainability, and convenience.
